891, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2042410, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 398616, "reply_to": 2042349, "tag": null, "text": "其实吧，如果你想在教室用电脑，续航不够也抢不到插座，这种情况的话你可以带个接线板去教室2333", "timestamp": 1625981053, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2042416, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 398616, "reply_to": 2042392, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 不不不，我的需求在于\n1、几乎一整天不在宿舍，充电机会少，所以要续航\n2、在pdf上做笔记，因此需要触屏pencil（以及直接用这种方式交那些电子版的作业）\n3、上A课做B事（指上课写其它课程的每周小论文），所以对于打字效率有需求", "timestamp": 1625981099, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2042605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 398616, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个需求 iPad 有啥满足不了的吗", "timestamp": 1625983115, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2042720, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 398616, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "捂脸还在考虑要不要上手iPad", "timestamp": 1625984591, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2046907, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 398616, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有虚拟机的", "timestamp": 1626022925, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 2, "pid": 398616, "reply": 22, "tag": null, "text": "所以iPad上可以刷win或者MacOS吗\n感觉iPadOS的生产力不大行", "timestamp": 1625979455, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626022925, "url": "", "vote": {}}}